<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
    <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css"
          integrity="sha384-rHyoN1iRsVXV4nD0JutlnGaslCJuC7uwjduW9SVrLvRYooPp2bWYgmgJQIXwl/Sp" crossorigin="anonymous"/>


    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ asset('favicon.ico') }}"/>

    <style type="text/css">

        .green {
            background-color: #93be46;
            color: white;
        }

        .main-content {
            max-width: 1024px;
            overflow-x: hidden
        }

        .bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 10px;
        }

        .image-container img {
            max-height: 360px;
        }

        .image-container {
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .marketing-container {
            text-align: center
        }
    </style>

    {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
</head>
<body>
<div class="main-content container-fluid">

    <div class="row">
        <div class="hidden-xs col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 ">

            <div style="overflow: hidden">

                <img src="{{ asset('assets/img/A1@1024.png') }}" alt="SmartSmile logo"
                     style="margin: 0 auto;display: block;">

            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg">

            <img src="{{ asset('assets/img/A1@300.png') }}" class="img-responsive" alt="SmartSmile logo"
                 style="margin: 0 auto;display: block;">

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg green" style="text-align:center">

            <h4 style="font-weight:bold">ПЕРВЫЙ В УКРАИНЕ</h4>
            <h4 style="font-weight:bold">5-НТР САЙТ ХОРОШЕГО НАСТРОЕНИЯ и</h4>
            <h4 style="font-weight:bold">ЭМОЦИОНАЛЬНОГО КОМФОРТА</h4>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">

            <a href="{{ path('app_index') }}">
                <img src="{{ asset('assets/img/A6@800.jpg') }}" class="img-responsive" alt="SmartSmile logo"
                     style="margin: 10px auto;display: block;">
            </a>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class=" green bar"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {% block body %}{% endblock %}

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class=" green bar"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12" style="text-align:center">
            <h4>ВОПРОСЫ И ПОЖЕЛАНИЯ ПОТРЕБИТЕЛЕЙ ПРИНИМАЕТ</h4>
            <address>
                <h4><strong>ООО «ОМНИФАРМА КИЕВ»</strong></h4>
                <h4>КИЕВ, ПРОСП. Н.БАЖАНА, 10А, 2 ЭТАЖ</h4>
                <h5>
                    <strong>
                        <a style="color:black;text-decoration:underline"
                           href="mailto:omnifarma-kiev@mail.ua">omnifarma-kiev@mail.ua</a>
                    </strong>
                </h5>
            </address>

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class=" green bar"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12" style="text-align:center">
            <h5>Добавка диетическая.</h5>
            <h5>Производитель: ОДО «ИНТЕРХИМ» (Украина).</h5>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

{% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}

</body>
</html>